via-violet-400 to-indigo-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent\">🗜️ 图片压缩</h1><p class=\"text-zinc-400\">免费、快速、隐私安全 — 所有处理均在浏览器本地完成</p><span class=\"inline-block mt-3 px-3 py-1 bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 text-xs font-medium rounded-full border border-green-500/20\">🔒 你的图片不会被上传到任何服务器</span></header><div class=\"max-w-[960px] mx-auto px-6 pb-12\"><div class=\"relative border-2 border-dashed rounded-2xl p-12 md:p-16 text-center cursor-pointer transition-all duration-200 border-zinc-700 bg-zinc-900/50 hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-indigo-500/[0.02]\"><span class=\"text-5xl block mb-4\">📁</span><div class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-2\">拖拽图片到这里，或点击上传</div><div class=\"text-sm text-zinc-500\">支持 JPEG、PNG、WebP、GIF、BMP 格式 · 也可直接 Ctrl+V 粘贴</div></div><input type=\"file\" accept=\"image/*\" multiple=\"\" style=\"position:fixed;top:-9999px;left:-9999px;width:0;height:0\" tabindex=\"-1\"/><div class=\"mt-6\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 p-5 bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\"><label class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-wider\">输出格式</label><select class=\"px-3 py-2.5 bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 rounded-lg text-zinc-100 text-sm outline-none focus:border-indigo-500 transition-colors\"><option value=\"image/webp\" selected=\"\">WebP（推荐）</option><option value=\"image/jpeg\">JPEG</option><option value=\"image/png\">PNG（无损）</option></select></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\"><label class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-wider\">压缩质量</label><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><input type=\"range\" min=\"1\" max=\"100\" class=\"flex-1 h-1.5 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full appearance-none cursor-pointer [&amp;::-webkit-slider-thumb]:appearance-none [&amp;::-webkit-slider-thumb]:w-5 [&amp;::-webkit-slider-thumb]:h-5 [&amp;::-webkit-slider-thumb]:bg-indigo-500 [&amp;::-webkit-slider-thumb]:rounded-full [&amp;::-webkit-slider-thumb]:shadow-[0_2px_8px_rgba(99,102,241,0.4)] [&amp;::-webkit-slider-thumb]:hover:scale-110 [&amp;::-webkit-slider-thumb]:transition-transform\" value=\"80\"/><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-400 min-w-[36px] text-right\">80<!-- -->%</span></div><div class=\"text-[11px] text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed mt-1\"><span class=\"text-zinc-400\">参考：</span><span class=\"\">40% 极限压缩</span> ·<span class=\"\">65% 网页配图</span> ·<span class=\"text-amber-400 font-medium\">80% 推荐</span> ·<span class=\"\">90% 高质量</span> ·<span class=\"\">100% 接近原图</span></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\"><label class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-wider\">调整尺寸（可选）</label><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><input type=\"number\" placeholder=\"宽\" min=\"1\" class=\"w-20 px-2.5 py-2 bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 rounded-lg text-zinc-100 text-sm outline-none focus:border-indigo-500 transition-colors\" value=\"\"/><button class=\"text-lg transition-colors text-indigo-500\" title=\"已锁定：修改宽度时高度自动按比例变化，图片不会变形\">🔗</button><input type=\"number\" placeholder=\"高\" min=\"1\" class=\"w-20 px-2.5 py-2 bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 rounded-lg text-zinc-100 text-sm outline-none focus:border-indigo-500 transition-colors\" value=\"\"/></div><div class=\"text-[11px] text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed\">🔗 <span class=\"text-zinc-400\">宽高比已锁定</span>，修改一侧尺寸时另一侧自动按比例调整，图片不会变形。留空则保持原始尺寸。</div></div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 mt-6\"></div><div class=\"text-center py-12 text-zinc-500\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-3\">🌄</div><div class=\"text-sm\">上传图片开始压缩</div></div></div><footer class=\"text-center py-8 px-6 text-zinc-600 text-xs border-t border-zinc-800/50\">纯浏览器端图片压缩工具 · 你的隐私我们守护</footer></main><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-853ff5b6bce5466c.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[8960,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n3:I[8191,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n4